#8000
The Avenue of the Gods~
  You stand on the broad Avenue of the Gods in the city of Kir Drax'in.  To
your north is the corner of the grand stadium of Kir Drax'in.  The Avenue forms
a junction with the city wall road immediately to your west.  To your south,
there is an ivy-covered marble doorway set into an otherwise dull brick wall.
