#8164
a Perfect Circle~
   The only way out is to the west, back through the large wrought-iron gates.
Here stands a gigantic stone platform chiseled from one solid piece of rock.
The enormous slab is at least as a yard thick and twenty-five yards in
diameter, it is a perfect circle.  Seems to have been here for thousands of
years, nobody knows how it got here.  There are burn marks, gouges, claw marks
and many other imperfections all over the stone.  Regardless of what it used
to be for when it was originally built, some folks use this to contain
dangerous encounters for various reasons.  At the center of the platform there
is a large demonic pentagram burned deep into the stone.
