#8167
The Stables~
   To the north you can see the main room of the barn.  Upward, there is a
well built set of stairs that leads up to the hay loft.  There are several
rows of stalls for individual horses.  There are feed bags, hay bails, and a
watering trough that runs along the backside of the stalls.  To the west there
is a large storage unit that holds saddles and saddle bags that belong to the
tenants of Kir Drax'in Lodge, each with a number that corresponds with it's
respective horse stall.
~
