a Dark and Dusty Hay Loft~
   Dust from all of the hay being tossed below to the lower barn area is
everywhere, as well as suspended in the still air.  There are stacks upon
stacks of hay lining all of the wills and piled to the ceiling.  Everything
seems to be perfectly aligned.  You notice, however, a gap in one of the large
stacks.  There is a pile of hay in the middle of the room.  Your only exit is
down the ladder back into the horse stall area.
