#8169
the Kir Drax'in Lodge Foyer~
   In the foyer you can go west back outside to the vestibule, or east through
large archway into the lodge's main lobby.  The ceilings are very high and
painted with scenes of battles won by the Kir Drax'in people against various
evil entities.  A particular scene catches your eye - that of a very large
reptilian creature towering over the city's buildings destroying houses,
shops, and swallowing adventurers whole.  The Behemoth has always been a
looming fear amongst the citizens of Kir Drax'in.  The floors are polished oak
and accented with marble tiles down the center leading to the lobby.
~
