#8171
Finn Elkheart's Bar and Lounge~
   To leave the bar, you will need to go back north where you came from.  The
main bar area is very dimly lit by lanterns at each table, which there are
twelve.  The ceiling is covered in copper tiles with a dark smoke stained oak
molding.  To the south you spot the bar, it is extremely long and spans the
width of the room, east to south.  There is a section of the bar that can be
lifted upward, to give access to the bartender To the west, you spot a large
bookshelf, only there are no books just various artifacts and stuffed
creatures.
~
