#8173
the Back Room~
   Finn's dimly lit back room houses some of his most prized treasures.  They
are locked away behind thick glass and steel barred cases around the room.
There is a single table in the middle of the room, it is covered in a deep red
felt fabric.  The table is in the shape of a octogon, which is surrounded by
eight padded, leather and oak chairs.
~
