2 8171 8171
E
cases~
   There are 3 extremely large cases on each wall.  Except for the wall with
the secret door back into the main bar.  Case one, contains an array of
daggers, swords, and other weapons.  Case two, contains spell books, scrolls,
and other magical texts.  Case three, contains the heads, some still blinking,
of slain monsters.  Seems this one is air tight and sound proof as you cannot
smell the rotting flesh or hear the screams of those heads that are still
alive.
~
S
#8174
the Kir Drax'in Lodge's Front Desk~
   At the front desk, you find plush carpet surrounding it.  The desk is more
of a counter, topped with beautiful marble and supported by a ornate carved
oak base.  Ceilings are extremely high and just as delicately engineered and
designed.  There is a large chandelier hanging down above this area.  The exit
west will take you back to the main lobby.  Heading north, and up the stairs
will bring you to the Dragon Suites.  Taking a stroll south will bring you to
the Four-Horsemen Suites.
~
