#8175
a Stairwell to the Four Horsemen Suites~
   You are at the base of the black-stained oak staircase leading up to the
Four Horsemen themed suites.  Everything that can be is wood and stained
black, except the carpet, which is the color of dried blood and made of a
durable woven hemp.  There are a few ornate brass lanterns hanging from the
tall ceiling.  Guessing from the look of this stairwell the rest of the wing
should prove ominous.  One possible escape is back to the front desk area where
it is comfortable and inviting.  The less appealing choice would be to ascend
the stairway to what looks to be a nightmare.
~
